      <title>日本央行前官员看到机会支付结果将促使三月加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/ex-boj-official-sees-chance-pay-results-to-prompt-march-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位前日本央行官员认为，在工资谈判的早期结果强劲后，该行政策委员会将抓住机会在周二结束负利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/ex-boj-official-sees-chance-pay-results-to-prompt-march-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 03:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
